### ============================================
### TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE
### ============================================
###
### 1. Make sure backend is running:
###    cd backend && npm run dev
###
### 2. Make sure MongoDB is running:
###    brew services start mongodb-community
###
### 3. Check .env file exists in backend folder with:
###    PORT=5000
###    MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/animal-rescue
###    JWT_SECRET=animal-rescue-secret
###
### 4. To use JWT Token:
###    - Run signup request first
###    - Run login request to get token
###    - Copy the "token" field from response
###    - Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN in requests above
###
### 5. For VS Code REST Client Extension:
###    - Install: humao.rest-client
###    - Click "Send Request" above any request
###
### 6. Common Issues:
###    - 400: Bad request - check JSON format
###    - 401: Unauthorized - token missing or invalid
###    - 500: Server error - check backend console
###    - Connection refused - backend not running
###
